author_ssm: Ted Casselman and Gail Malmgreen, 2000-2001. Folder contents for Box 15, Folder 4 revised by Hillel Arnold, March 2009.
abstract_ssm: Cleveland Robinson (1914-1995) was an African American trade union leader and civil rights activist who served as Secretary-Treasurer of the United Auto Workers of America, District 65, from 1952-1992. The collection contains correspondence, miscellaneous documents, ephemera and clippings.
